active measures are a form of intelligence including 
disinformation through which one power seeks to discredit another 
or to build up its own image through covert activities 
according to the fbi the americansoviet council was founded by 
the communist party of the united states in 1943 and operates as a 
soviet front group which provides the soviets with an excellent 
conduit to promote its active measures campaigns meet with us 
persons of influence spot and assess us persons for recruitment 
