100 or more per acre for property 
what bothers me is that what i did with chairman macdonald was 
improper he said 
besides giving macdonald 25000 and a car brown said he paid 
the tribal chairman several 5000 increments in 100 bills 
the payments were arranged by macdonalds son who called brown 
when his father needed money and used the word golf balls as a 
code for money 
in another taped conversation played for the committee brown is 
heard talking to the junior macdonald on dec 14 1988 
were all three of us three musketeers shoulder to shoulder 
macdonald says in reference to browns question as to whether he 
