bingo operation separate from the mob he answered this committee 
would be sending flowers to my family 
the bureau of indian affairs is useless in helping the indians 
he said for example when the fbi came to his reservation to 
inquire about the bingo operation he simply told them to get off 
the property and they did 
organized crime families view indian reservations they same way 
they once looked at cuba he said wide open no regulations no 
controls 
the solution he said is that a police force should be formed 
under federal control that could supply the indians with information 
they need about the bingo managers and could go in and look at the 
books 
