its western neighbor over the weapons research 
the newspaper neues deutschland said any government doing such 
research is not seriously interested in seeing success at the 
upcoming vienna conventional weapons talks 
these parties are at the most using these talks to cover up 
major disarmament projects the newspaper said in a commentary 
