on wednesday to the un chief breathes new life into the peace 
plan initiated by president oscar arias of costa rica who received 
the nobel peace prize for his efforts in 1987 
plans for the force have already been drafted un officials 
said on condition of anonymity and spain canada and west germany 
have agreed to contribute observers 
